song.title: Low Hanging Sky
song.info: This tune was composed for the best pc-diskmag that was made in Russia at this moment - "Armor Of Gods" issue 4. 16-bit version was released as a single after several requests from people who wanted it. Warhawk asked me if I can write something in "Enigma" style. I think this tune is not like "Enigma" very much, but it is kinda mellow and trip-hoppish, and it has very clean sound because of the samples.
